    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your focus and connection to magic have increased. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You no longer require material components to cast spells, unless a cost is indicated for the component or the component is consumed.</li>\n<li>When you cast a spell as a ritual, the casting time increases by 1 minute instead of 10 minutes.</li>\n<li>You have advantage on Intelligence (Arcana) checks made to identify spells.</li>\n<li>As a bonus action, you can cast a spell that has a casting time of 1 action that targets only you.</li>\n</ul>",
